node.text: If your kid wakes up at night to drink some water, of course, it’s more convenient to leave a glass of water somewhere near their bed. If there’s no bedside table in their room, you can create a small stand for a drink with a 3D pen. This way, you will prevent water from spilling, and a cup will always be in a safe place. If your kids love using too much liquid soap when washing their hands, try this easy hack with hair bands. For those parents whose kids love using too much toilet paper, we also have a solution😅 Stick a piece of colored tape to the wall to show how much toilet paper they should tear off. Create a fantastic washable coloring book for your kids, so they will never get bored. Especially in the car! There aren’t that many things to do there, right ;) Don’t forget to buy some whiteboard markers and an eraser.
